    "stac_version": "1.1.0",
    "description": "This dataset contains the products used for calibration and validation of the Observational Products for End-Users from Remote Sensing Analysis (OPERA) Coregistered Single-Look Complex (CSLC) from Sentinel-1 validated product. The CSLC-S1 product is derived from Copernicus Sentinel-1A and Sentinel-1B Interferometric Wide (IW) SLC data, provided by the European Space Agency.  OPERA CSLC-S1 products are available over North America which includes USA and US Territories within 200 km from the US border, Canada, and all mainland countries from the southern US border down to and including Panama.",
